     </section>
       <section>
<list>
<item>
<name><![CDATA[Browses (for <OBJECT> use either the <BROWSE> pointer or the name of the browse)]]></name>
</item>
<item>
<name><![CDATA[Forms (for <OBJECT> use either the <FORM> pointer or the name of the form)]]></name>
</item>

</list>
       </section>

       <section><description><![CDATA[The <OBJECT>.MARK_RECORD() method marks the current record.
]]></description></section>
       
       
   </sections>
   <sections>
       <section><title>Example</title>
            <description>This script marks the current record.</description>
            <example><![CDATA[Parentform.mark_record()]]></example>
       </section>
   </sections>
